DALLAH-CAR RENTAL USSC POA INSTRUCTORS PR4472999. FY16 ICASS RECAP INVOICE 1957.0 - KENYA. INCLE TSCTP : Law enforcement, security sector ref. PR4549914-TPC Morocco Snr Corrections Advisor

description.narrative: Combat transnational terrorism, especially from al-Qa'ida, its affiliates, and adherents using a strategic counterterrorism approach that focuses on 1) countering violent extremism; 2) building the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutions to address threats within their own borders; and 3) building stronger relationships with our partners around the world – in order to engage in a broader, more comprehensive counterterrorism effort that treats civilian institutions, to include the justice sector and law enforcement, as a critical part of building effective partner capacity to counter terrorism.

This award strives to combat transnational terrorism, counter violent extremism, build the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutuions, and build stronger relationships with our partners around the world. This includes TRAIN, EVAL & OTH RELATED ACT[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. Information has been redacted in accordance with the two principled exceptions defined in the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act (FATAA) of 2016: the health and security of implementing partners, and the national interest of the United States.. Train, Eval & Oth Related Act. Jose V. Amado[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. TRAIN, EVAL & OTH RELATED ACT[Covers miscellaneous contractual services such as A&E contracts and IT site preparation by the PBA, GSA, and commercial contracts, among other things.].
